section#drawer-object
  h2 The Drawer Object
  p.
    #[strong Note:]
    The Drawer Object will be fixed off-screen when screen is smaller than 720px.
    Extra Javascript functionality may be added to show it on command (as seen in the figure below).
  figure.docs-figure
    input.docs-btn--md#drawer-check(type="checkbox" value="open demo drawer")
    label(for="drawer-check") open demo drawer
      small  (only relevant on XS/S screens)
    div.o-Drawer
      h1 drawer heading
      p drawer content
    pre.docs-pre.docs-pre--has-md.
      &lt;div class="#[u o-Drawer]#[mark   #[u.-d-i o-Drawer--open]]"&gt;
        &lt;h1&gt;drawer heading&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;drawer content&lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
